In this thread I will be sharing some of my favourite posts of Hakan Rotmwrt, the best frogtwitter poster and man of arcane knowledge, pre-scientific mind, and biomic supremacism

To call his worldview "undemocratic", "fascist" or any other word in the English language would be an insult to his beliefs.

The last men who shared his "philosophy" have died hundreds of thousands of years ago.

Absolute virility, esoteric hatred of seemingly regular things...

Hakan was able to connect all manner of things, for him no such thing as "distinction" or "timespace" existed. He looked at the world as one giant organism and could see the webs of connections between any two things.

Island peoples and nazis, modern celebrities and dravidians

While seemingly coming from the primordial past, Hakan had great scientific knowledge and many ideas that sadly this millennium would deem "unethical".

Microchimerization used to create new races of humans, mixed with tigers, whales, horses... Demonic Egyptian gods reborn today.

The best thing about Hakan is that every single one of his posts is an entrance to a rabbit hole:

every concept or idea he mentions does truly exist, and does take days to properly research (and leads to hundreds of other curious topics)

A favourite of mine were always his takes on the Aboriginal Australian peoples, which seemed to be one of his most beloved ones.

Here he gives a take on UFOs I haven't seen anywhere else, UFOs as astral projections of Aboriginal men who are asleep
